^ a b c Reddinger, Paige (16 March 2015). "Domenico De Sole’s Latest Role: Chairman Of Sotheby’s". fashionweekdaily.com. Retrieved 18 March 2015. 
^ "Rickie De Sole and Derek Webster". New York Times. 6 July 2012. Retrieved 18 March 2015. 







 
